These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, asparagus
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, sports
1. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | asparagus | nectarine |
| Movie-Genre     | sports    | adventure   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, gospel
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, artichoke
1. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | salsa        |
| Food      | grapefruit  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, freelancer
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, orange
1. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
2. the freelancer is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Job   | freelancer    | librarian |
| Color   | apricot | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, ebony
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, french
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the french is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Color   | pink      | ebony |
| Nationality       | argentine | french    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, skateboard
1. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Beverage           | sprite | soy-milk |
| Transport   | skateboard    | car         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Job       | dressmaker | accountant  |
| Hobby   | woodworking  | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, tram
