.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, july
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, western
1. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |
| Birthday           | august | july |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller    |

