The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, classical
1. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up   |
| Music-Genre         | folk | classical |

