.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bolivar
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the prince-smoker##1
2. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Cigar   | bolivar       | prince   |
| Pet   | cat | hedgehog |

